"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Gm; The HackerDudez team would like to introduce its manifest to the world. We believe together we will build the new era of what we call education 3.0. Read and enjoy this manifest. With your support, WGMI.\\n\\n## What is HackerDudez?\\n\\nBlockchain technology and Web 3.0 are evolving the way people interact with each other in communities and industries are getting disrupted by rebel founders who want to change the equation. We believe the current educational system is a bug in mind of new generation and we want to change the learning process to a free and fun in which result in wisdom and wealth for all the parties involved in the ecosystem.\\n\\nHackerdudez will be a community of pioneers who believe Education at all levels should be free for the human being. We would like to create a progressive DAO (decentralized Autonomous Organization) in which revolutionizes global education from k-12 to higher education and Skillful training in the creator economy decade.\\n\\n## Vision\\n\\nWe believe industrial age of education system which has been dragged till now is a shame for the human history. We can not simply put people with different talents, skills and passion into cubes and force them to achieve compulsory grades. It is a murder of talents which happens now in our school systems.\\n\\nWe believe great quality of higher education should be free. It is not fair that only wealthy people can afford high tuition for top rated universities in the world. Good teachers can earn much higher while still they can offer their courses free to the whole world.\\n\\nWe believe in opportunity for all. We believe in borderless education available for every human being in our universe and with the help of our backers and web 3.0 technology now it is a great time to practice our vision.\\n\\n## Mission\\n\\nHackerDudez mission is to build an educational metaverse in which education is accessible for all in free and fun to learn. It will also help students to earn money as well while they are studying and learning. the rewards will be based on your competency and social credit in your chosen community and classes as a student.\\n\\n## Why now?\\n\\nHackerDudez is not just an idea. It roots in the mind of its founder for over a decade. During the quarter 4 of 2017, We saw more people got interested and entered to the crypto currency space which is one part of blockchain and web 3.0 technologies. In 2021, the world heard about NFTs which opened a completely new business model for pioneers and fans of artists, creators and also a push for DAO enthusiasts though we are still very early in this era; Meanwhile Creator economy is thriving and more platforms will pop up to give ownership and member management under the control of their respective creatives. more skilful people will become leaders in their communities and creativity will blossom with the help of new infrastructure and services for the creators.\\n\\nWe think now, We are at the intersection of proper time for creator economy + DAO + NFT; While DAOs are a very new and unfamiliar term for many people including tech early adopters(!) but we want to be those pioneers who shapes the future of education. We see teachers as beautiful creators in this world. Their creation is to train and teach beautiful mind to serve humanity.\\n\\n## Teachers as Creators\\n\\nWe think it is ridiculous that in most of the counties, wages for teachers is so low while they have one of the most valuable careers in the world. We believe teachers should be wealthy as well so they can serve their students with more care and dedication. Salute to all teachers around the world. You are stars of human being history and we want to change this situation.\\n\\nIn this area, we would like to morph teachers role more into creator and make their knowledge free, fun and understandable for their students and fans. Either it is a topic in math for high school or a biology subject in the university or a mastery of a craft, teachers need proper tools and ecosystem to transfer their knowledge and we want to be that platform.\\n\\n## Students as curators\\n\\nWe believe students should be active in the process of learning. Hackerdudez DAO and platform will provide students tools and environment so they can build up their credit and reputation and also help other students and sometimes teachers as well to create a richer friendly and fun environment to learn any topic. Furthermore they can earn real money to reach their financial freedom as well just by being a great student and build an on-chain reputation and activity in their communities. Isn't that cool?\\n\\n## NFT Entrance \\n\\nNFTs have opened a new window for community designers to create robust, sustain and durable communities in which members can earn by curation and participation in the activities.\\n\\nWe are sure with the help of web 3.0 technology stacks, We can bring our long vision to the reality. We have found NFT community very supportive and open minded when it comes to new ideas or brave moves. We hope positivity and warmness of NFT enthusiasts streams towards this beautiful DAO. WGMI ;)\",\"timestamp\":1637218139,\"title\":\"HackerDudez Manifest\"},\"digest\":\"Ojt2_7B_v-S8aG3VWTjbdRsBEvIYUerPbDE01Gj4qFY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xECEB8653B2D3d497F683a94373c7def1188220F6\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"0K1MYpwTzYN7OaXhNgiStozthgzkiPJSZvnL2UiYC2k\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"_l91erait5NY-5gLUCgHYJq6vru4RjOmzu3jM8nzZiw\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"XH9dJDWLuV8JWj1LvAofQYRpZWg7-6h9q0tn8s_Icu0uu9zevZIY3KypKeb8U5UAEB_4iu7lJBJwrkEsMWk7cA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x092e1142fc3ac05ffcb61b5dc74bb903ad418565ca67f8dc0e4692ba265ef44c02d2a147f49f0c4fdbd30fd169bc4314950eaa0e9fb403224526ef3aa3b3f3001c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"0K1MYpwTzYN7OaXhNgiStozthgzkiPJSZvnL2UiYC2k\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"_l91erait5NY-5gLUCgHYJq6vru4RjOmzu3jM8nzZiw\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"sL8EzuVr8cmffRvzgcxGiIcTFmUQiyu_dBqB_EQOKXw\"}"